.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/ul0gic/fail2zig/issues
.UE .
.PP
Known limitations in v0.1.0:
.IP \(bu 2
Daemon mode (background process) is not yet implemented; run under a process
supervisor.
.IP \(bu 2
Hot-reload (\fBfail2zig-client reload\fR) is implemented at the IPC level but
the daemon-side handler is a stub; a restart is required to pick up config
changes.
.IP \(bu 2
Per-jail bantime increment settings are parsed but only the \fB[defaults]\fR
values take effect.
.
.SH HISTORY
fail2zig 0.1.0 was the first public release, April 2026.
